# RTM Hello — Cursor Rules

A minimal calculator project demonstrating TDD with Requirement Traceability.

**Read `docs/RTM-guide.md`** for the full methodology.

## Key Rules
- Every test MUST have `@pytest.mark.req("REQ-CALC-XXX")`
- Add requirements to `docs/RTM.md` before writing tests
- Verify: `python scripts/req_coverage.py --strict`

## Tech Stack
Python · pytest · AST-based marker extraction
